      <title>法国失业率意外下降 为马克龙带来助力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/french-unemployment-unexpectedly-declines-in-boost-for-macron</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国第二季度失业率意外下降，表明总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 不受欢迎的劳动力市场改革正在取得一些成效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/french-unemployment-unexpectedly-declines-in-boost-for-macron</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国反对党解散，成立新政党，力争赢得选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/disbanded-thai-opposition-group-eyes-2027-poll-win-as-new-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周早些时候被法院解散的泰国反对党成员已重组为人民党，其新领导人设定了三年内在东南亚国家组建一党政府的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/disbanded-thai-opposition-group-eyes-2027-poll-win-as-new-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 09 Aug 2024 05:25:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
